<a:ModificationDate>1678355921</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>XE96576</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Payment location strings are generated that are used once and remain in another state awaiting the purging process. It is necessary to index by said status so that online operations, which generate bookmarks for new payments, are not penalized when recovering those payments that have not yet been located.</a:Comment>
